            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility"> ¶ [A letter was read from Mr Berg, the representative of the French Acclimatisation Society at the Isle of Bourbon, offering to forward anything from that island which the Council might think desirab...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">62.05.00e</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Achille Berg</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letter not found. See <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Age</seg> (Melbourne), 19 July 1862, p. 5, in the report of the meeting of the Council of the Acclimatisation Society of Victoria held on 17 July. The letter is dated to May on the basis that this is the latest date it could have been written to arrive in Melbourne in early July (a vessel arriving on 2 July from Mauritius left there on 17 May; 'Shipping intelligence', <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Argus</seg>, 9 July 1862, p. 4).</p>
               </note>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>[A letter was read from Mr Berg, the representative of the French Acclimatisation Society at the Isle of Bourbon, offering to forward anything from that island which the Council might think desirable, in exchange for the native productions of Victoria. This letter was addressed to Dr <seg style="">Mueller</seg>, and he was requested to reply to it.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Reply not found.</p>
               </note>]</p>
         </div>
